The free shuttle, every 15 minutes, to and from the Spanish Steps was a huge help.	We were moved, but the request from our travel agent for an early check-in and back room had been totally ignored until our arrival.	The hotel runs a free shuttle to Spanish Steps every 20 minutes, however, which really helps.	Also ignored was our request to have an upper level floor in the back and away from the sounds of streetcars in the front of the hotel.	The staff was most helpful to our every request and made the four of us feel special.	By the way, transfer is gently provided by the hotel every half hour which helps a lot.